              Exploring different technologies and solving various challenges
            </p>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-brand-gradient mx-auto mt-4 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
