          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            I'm always interested in working on exciting projects and solving challenging problems.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
